meeting a woman online."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Животът на Интернет-плейбой излиза извън контрол, след като се запознава с жена онлайн."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Не пара","runtime":83,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"У Харриса всё отлично - веселые друзья, интересная работа, перспектива повышения и нескончаемая череда красивых девушек благодаря приложению для знакомств. Но когда свидание с одной из них заканчивается не так, как он привык, его идеальная жизнь быстро выходит из-под контроля."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Cita con el miedo","runtime":85,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"La vida de un playboy que usa internet para quedar con mujeres cambia radicalmente después de conocer a una de ellas."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Het leven van Harris, een via internet datende playboy verandert wanneer hij online de vrouw Riley leert kennen. Na een onenightstand denkt ze dat ze zijn vriendin is en omdat ze niet om kan gaan met afwijzing volgen al gauw dreigementen. Daarbij komt hij in de problemen op zijn werk en met de politie."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":90,"tagline":"Elle meurt d'envie de vous rencontrer.","homepage":"","overview":"Harris enchaîne les conquêtes d’un soir grâce aux applis de rencontre et une approche bien ficelée. Tout marche comme sur des roulettes jusqu’au moment où il rencontre la belle et séduisante Riley. Mais contrairement aux autres filles, Riley n’a pas envie d’une simple aventure avec Harris. Obsession, manipulation, intrusion… la vie d’Harris ne tarde pas à prendre un tournant cauchemardesque."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Cita con el miedo","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Harris es un alérgico al compromiso profesional que usa su aplicación de contactos favorita para acostarse cada noche con una mujer diferente. Un día tiene un encuentro con Riley, un auténtico pibón que a partir de entonces empieza a enviarle mensajes continuos y obsesivos, segura de que es demasiado sexy para que él la rechace."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Atração Obsessiva","runtime":83,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Harris é um mulherengo nato e sempre marca encontros por meio de um aplicativo. A vida dele foge do controle quando ele conhece Riley, uma garota que começa a manifestar um comportamento obsessivo."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Życie nastolatka wymyka się spod kontroli po spotkaniu z kobietą online."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Harris hat alles, was ein junger Mann in seinem Leben braucht: Einen gutbezahlten Job in einer angesagten Agentur, viele Freunde, reichlich Zeit für Videospiele und dank einer Dating-App auch jede Menge unverbindlichen Sex. Nahezu jeden Abend trifft er sich mit neuen Matches und schafft es, mit ein- und derselben simplen aber charmanten Masche, die Mädels ins Bett zu bekommen. Alles läuft perfekt für ihn - bis er die hübsche Riley kennenlernt. Denn anders als seine sonstigen Dates, verschwindet die junge Studentin nicht einfach wieder aus seinem Leben. Sie scheint geradezu besessen von Harris zu sein und lässt ihm keine Ruhe mehr. Schnell verwandelt sich sein traumhaftes Leben in einen Albtraum."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ένας νεαρός που αρέσκεται στο να κλείνει ερωτικά ραντεβού απ'το ίντερνετ θα δει την ζωή του να βγαίνει εκτός ελέγχου μετά την γνωριμία του με την Riley!"},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Harrisilla tuntuu olevan kaikkea: hyvä työpaikka, paljon ystäviä ja aktiivinen seksielämä eri deittisovellusten ansiosta. Mutta kaikki muuttuu, kun pariksi osuu Riley. Toisin kuin Harris, Riley ei hae yhden yön seuraa, ja vaikka Harris alkuun pitää Rileya vain hieman takertuvana, alkaa karmiva totuus pian paljastua. Käsikirjoittaja David Chirchirillo tekee kiehtovan ja tuoreen tulkinnan pieleen menevistä treffeistä. Se saa ajattelemaan kahdesti ennen kuin pyyhkäiset oikealle."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Bad Match","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Harris è un giovane che sembra avere tutto: un buon lavoro, un sacco di amici e una vita sessuale molto attiva grazie a una serie di app per incontri. Ha inoltre imparato come destreggiarsi con i primi appuntamenti, a portarli a termine come vuole e a non cadere mai nell'errore di un secondo incontro. Tuttavia, tutto cambia quando incontra Riley. A differenza di Harris, Riley non è alla ricerca di una sola notte di sesso ma vuole molto di più. Inizialmente Harris la considera solo molto appiccicosa ma ben presto scoprirà qualcosa di molto più sinistro."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Harris har allt man kan önska sig – ett fantastiskt jobb, massor av vänner och ett aktivt sexliv tack vare alla datingappar. Men det förändras när han träffar Riley. Till skillnad från Harris letar inte Riley efter ett one-night-stand och till en början antar Harris bara att hon är klängig, men han får snart reda på att sanningen är mycket värre än så."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"错配","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"一名网络约会花花公子在网上认识一名女子后，生活变得失控。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"戀愛進行弒","runtime":0,"tagline":"當花花公子遇上恐怖情人，令人難以忘懷的「豔遇」即將展開…","homepage":"","overview":"哈里斯是個流連於交友軟體的花花公子，總是在一夜情結束後找盡各種理由消失，比起談戀愛他更喜歡花時間在工作和電玩上。某日，哈里斯一如既往地在交友軟體上左右尋歡，並與超辣女子萊利配對成功，但是萊利並不向其他女孩一樣好擺脫，哈里斯也漸漸發現他的生活因為她的出現開始分崩離析…"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Čini se da Harris (Cutmore-Scott) ima sve – odličan posao, puno prijatelja, a zahvaljujući internetu i sajtovima za upoznavanje i aktivni seksualni život. Ali sve se mijenja od trena kada uz pomoć interneta upozna nametljivu Riley (Simmons) koja za razliku od Harrisa nije u potrazi za kratkom avanturom i odbije napustiti njegov život nakon jedne noći. Nakon što njegovi profili na društvenim mrežama budu hakirani, uslijedit će niz teških optužbi na Harrisov račun, pa će biti prisiljen spoznati krajnje granice svog zdravog razuma. Predstavnici zakona će odbiti povjerovati da je Harrisa jedna naizgled nevina djevojka uspjela potpuno izluditi…"},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"배드 매치","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"戀愛進行弒","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"哈里斯是個流連於交友軟體的花花公子，總是在一夜情結束後找盡各種理由消失，比起談戀愛他更喜歡花時間在工作和電玩上。某日，哈里斯一如既往地在交友軟體上左右尋歡，並與超辣女子萊利配對成功，但是萊利並不向其他女孩一樣好擺脱，哈里斯也漸漸發現他的生活因為她的出現開始分崩離析…"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Cuidado com o amor à primeira vista.","homepage":"","overview":"A vida de um playboy que namora pela internet sai do controle depois de conhecer uma mulher online."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":674358,"adult":false,"title":"Bad Boy","video":false,"overview":"The rise and fall of a soccer club owner, discovering the harsh reality of the sport, often connected with crime and fraud.","genre_ids":[28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1906,"vote_count":40,"poster_path":"/zbeuzetcJN1gnV0tdEgOMvzjvjX.jpg","release_date":"2020-02-21","vote_average":4.813,"backdrop_path":"/mWFHzbF23ps1vEh56W3xOJetHvA.jpg","original_title":"Bad Boy","original_language":"pl"},{"id":414977,"adult":false,"title":"Sam","video":false,"overview":"The journey of young, handsome New York City playboy Sam Wellman - man’s man and professional woman hater – and his relationship with Doc, his best (and only!) friend. One strange, drunken night Sam stumbles into an Old Curiosity Shop, where the elderly proprietor offers him tea along with sage advice on treasuring “the female of the species”. Sam awakens the next morning to find himself transformed into a woman.","genre_ids":[35,14,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.1277,"vote_count":71,"poster_path":"/yhi43UFo5DjksahZ8N5TUYDavPj.jpg","release_date":"2015-04-21","vote_average":5.225,"backdrop_path":"/zLNb7g7uNOjxhITXkvxwiWb4o7l.jpg","original_title":"Sam","original_language":"en"},{"id":665052,"adult":false,"title":"This Is Paris","video":false,"overview":"Meet the real Paris Hilton for the very first time as she embarks on a journey of healing and reflection, reclaiming her true identity along the way.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2674,"vote_count":48,"poster_path":"/44nWhN7Zkyi86K2waw7beJW8l9A.jpg","release_date":"2020-09-14","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/gmGJtBKnhf7FvhQGK9MCkPQQbjA.jpg","original_title":"This Is Paris","original_language":"en"},{"id":27881,"adult":false,"title":"Zombie Island Massacre","video":false,"overview":"Americans on vacation in the Caribbean take a tour of a nearby island at night and watch a local voodoo ritual. Soon after, they find themselves stranded on the island and under attack by unseen foes. One by one they meet violent ends.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2638,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/xuxXePMmZ7Xptepi7jtx0w04MLD.jpg","release_date":"1984-11-20","vote_average":3.384,"backdrop_path":"/sOutDF02hSuaXrLc4hwrtcbyYcb.jpg","original_title":"Zombie Island Massacre","original_language":"en"},{"id":474273,"adult":false,"title":"The Problem with Apu","video":false,"overview":"In the history of “The Simpsons,” few characters outside the title family have had as much cultural impact as Apu Nahasapeemapetilon, the Springfield convenience store owner. Comedian Hari Kondabolu is out to show why that might be a problem.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2634,"vote_count":48,"poster_path":"/sWsDV2D4HbRyfXMaWOTJYGIQwkl.jpg","release_date":"2017-11-18","vote_average":4.8,"backdrop_path":"/4cWXJUtLEdGIn15cmiHjEcsMiWf.jpg","original_title":"The Problem with Apu","original_language":"en"},{"id":47467,"adult":false,"title":"Kill Speed","video":false,"overview":"KILL SPEED is a high-octane, youth oriented, TOP GUN meets FAST & FURIOUS tale about best friends who fly home-built, high-tech planes to deliver Mexican manufactured crystal meth throughout rural California in order to fund their Hollywood, rock-star lifestyle.","genre_ids":[80,28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.539,"vote_count":34,"poster_path":"/w64IOlFCuM2s7XRqW3pO5wTeHg6.jpg","release_date":"2010-07-02","vote_average":4.1,"backdrop_path":"/qySEOp4MLscb9JDl89ooUJKpbVn.jpg","original_title":"Kill Speed","original_language":"en"},{"id":328480,"adult":false,"title":"Kept Woman","video":false,"overview":"Jessica and her fiancé Evan just moved from the city into their dream home on a quiet suburban street. Soon after, Jessica catches her seemingly friendly new neighbor, Simon, in a strange lie and can't let her suspicions rest. The danger escalates when Simon lures her inside his home and imprisons Jessica in his secret bunker, meticulously decorated in the idealized style of the 1950's.","genre_ids":[53,10770,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.257,"vote_count":77,"poster_path":"/yHlqPeZ31TACwmFaAl6gygGIPGf.jpg","release_date":"2015-02-28","vote_average":6.416,"backdrop_path":"/9tVTKBCoEluEXtp06mTxJSUhLTI.jpg","original_title":"Kept Woman","original_language":"en"},{"id":229182,"adult":false,"title":"The Harvest","video":false,"overview":"After becoming orphaned, a lonely girl moves in with her grandparents and tries to befriend a sick, bed-ridden boy next door, despite his mother’s strong objections. Her persistence leads to a friendship, but during secret visits, she uncovers dark secrets in the boy's home.","genre_ids":[27,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7008,"vote_count":216,"poster_path":"/he6abiplc1atXbN7OztQAiZoYU.jpg","release_date":"2015-04-10","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/g2AVuSgZHuTntU8P4nXYqEYOSXU.jpg","original_title":"The Harvest","original_language":"en"},{"id":515114,"adult":false,"title":"Honey: Rise Up and Dance","video":false,"overview":"Street dancer Skyler comes out of the shadow of her trained dancer sister, Tosha, & joins a dance competition with the Honey dance studio; the prize is a college scholarship.","genre_ids":[10402,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4339,"vote_count":107,"poster_path":"/gzxUNGk79dHk2mUb5HrhvooHScV.jpg","release_date":"2018-04-03","vote_average":6.949,"backdrop_path":"/6lvbLqT8CZWebjZNmtOB1xrWkaY.jpg","original_title":"Honey: Rise Up and Dance","original_language":"en"},{"id":399725,"adult":false,"title":"Ideal Home","video":false,"overview":"A couple is going through marital troubles made worse when a previously unknown grandson shows up.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6723,"vote_count":280,"poster_path":"/bmXBT2uL4HQGimyfy5iu4ESnEaJ.jpg","release_date":"2018-06-21","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/ku8W8VGN4RxpBAUw1c1ZJgQtqQp.jpg","original_title":"Ideal Home","original_language":"en"},{"id":265010,"adult":false,"title":"The Canal","video":false,"overview":"A man who suspects his wife is cheating on him begins having nightmarish visions of an evil presence that he believes inhabits his house.","genre_ids":[27,9648,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8454,"vote_count":452,"poster_path":"/5c4FFLSUx4ZBqcS2rq5CLVJdY9E.jpg","release_date":"2014-10-10","vote_average":5.762,"backdrop_path":"/8OfuPvpLLd9FhVxV7B6bC51JD84.jpg","original_title":"The Canal","original_language":"en"},{"id":10961,"adult":false,"title":"Behind the Mask: The Rise of Leslie Vernon","video":false,"overview":"The next great psycho horror slasher has given a documentary crew exclusive access to his life as he plans his reign of terror over the sleepy town of Glen Echo, all the while deconstructing the conventions and archetypes of the horror genre for them.","genre_ids":[35,27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5875,"vote_count":499,"poster_path":"/vie8a3z219Zsw81eAsM58B6VFEn.jpg","release_date":"2006-08-29","vote_average":6.454,"backdrop_path":"/w6mr3tvckNmlt5EMIBlsnI1YWnl.jpg","original_title":"Behind the Mask: The Rise of Leslie Vernon","original_language":"en"},{"id":14138,"adult":false,"title":"Black Water","video":false,"overview":"Based on true events, Grace, her boyfriend Adam, and her younger sister, Lee, are on holiday in Northern Australia when they decide to take a tour down a river. As they drift into a swamp, their boat suddenly capsizes. Stranded in the flooded swamp, the three tourists must figure out what to do to survive as they realize they are being watched through the black water.","genre_ids":[12,18,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0703,"vote_count":376